/ Calling the SubInputAndExtractOperandsAndOperator subroutine. (Task 3.1)
JnS SubInputAndExtractOperandsAndOperator

/ Calling the SubCal subroutine. (Task 3.2)
JnS SubCal

/ Calling the SubTextOutput subroutine. (Task 3.3)
JnS SubTextOutput

/ Calling the SubClearDisplay subroutine. (Task 3.4)
JnS SubClearDisplay

/ Calling the SubPaintChar subroutine. (Task 3.5)
Load DigitFontAddr
Add NEXTDIGIT 
Store PaintCharCharacter 
Load PIXELOFROW2COL2 
Store PaintCharDisplay 
JnS SubPaintChar 

/ Calling the SubPrintCalResultToDisplay subroutine. (Task 3.6)
JnS SubPrintCalResultToDisplay

/ This is the end of the main program.
Halt

